Rain, rain, go away.
Come again another day.
Mommy wants to play.
Rain, rain, go away.
Rain, rain, go away.
Come again another day.
Brother wants to play.
Rain, rain, go away.
Rain, rain, go away.
Come again another day.
Sister wants to play.
Rain, rain, go away.
Rain, rain, go away.
