	<Lesson>
		<Title>My Shadow</Title>
		<Author>Sao Mai Training Team</Author>
		<Description>By Robert Louis Stevenson</Description>
		<ExpectedSpeed>180</ExpectedSpeed>
		<ExpectedPoint>95</ExpectedPoint>
		<TextToType>I have a little shadow that goes in and out with me,
And what can be the use of him is more than I can see.
He is very, very like me from the heels up to the head;
And I see him jump before me, when I jump into my bed.
